title: Rachel Dratch / Raynaud's Phenomenon
description: Sean's experience being stuck on a plane for nine hours is Priyanka's worst nightmare. A listener calls in about a time his peepee went poopoo. Rachel Dratch shares the history of her iconic Debbie Downer character and the time she broke a bone because of the Brady Bunch. Priyanka uncovers how Rachel's relationship drama played a role with her Raynaud's.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
